# Admin routes
1.Route to render the admin page                 "/admin" 
2.Route to render the user registration form     "/userRegister"
3.Route to add the new user database             "/userRegister"
4.Route to render the form to add new book       "/admin/addBook"
5.Route to add new book database                 "/admin/addBook"
6.Route to update the book :                     "/index/:id"
7.Route to delete the book :                     "/index/:id"
8.Route to render the update book form :         "/index/:id/updateBook"
9.Rout to accept borrow request                  "/admin/acceptRequest"
10.Route to accept the return request.           "/admin/returnRequest"
